{
  "id": "RAW_84a0e8",
  "title": "首个多模态统一 CoT 奖励模型来了，奖励能力大幅跃升，已全面开源",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkwODU2OTQyNQ==&mid=2247494651&idx=1&sn=9a3dfd8a29b1472243726b2e42f55c6b&subscene=0",
  "date": "2025-05-13 10:36:00",
  "author": "腾讯混元",
  "siteName": "腾讯混元",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <mp-common-videosnap class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_live_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpvideosnap\" data-headimgurl=\"https://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/Y3WgNLFjO0e1rbGnQDFTLKdL1uAeeMVqqicdyVkLBicfXdz04ecGicUxQ/0\" data-username=\"v2_060000231003b20faec8c6eb8f1fc3d6cb02e835b077d30f0f482bdbb4c0d99547aa16a4af80@finder\" data-nickname=\"腾讯混元\" data-desc=\"将在05月13日 19:30 直播\" data-type=\"live\" data-intro=\"多模态奖励模型也能深度思考\" data-noticeid=\"finderlivenotice-v2_060000231003b20faec8c6eb8f1fc3d6cb02e835b077d30f0f482bdbb4c0d99547aa16a4af80@finder-1747017330423560-983894029\" data-status=\"0\"></mp-common-videosnap>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;visibility: visible;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在多模态大模型快速发展的当下，如何精准评估其生成内容的质量，正成为多模态大模型与人类偏好对齐的核心挑战。然而，当前主流多模态奖励模型往往只能直接给出评分决策，或仅具备浅层推理能力，缺乏对复杂奖励任务的深入理解与解释能力，在高复杂度场景中常出现 “失真失准”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">那么，奖励模型是否也能具备像人类一样的深度思考能力？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">近日，腾讯混元与上海 AI Lab、复旦大学、上海创智学院联合提出全新研究工作 UnifiedReward-Think，构建出首个具备长链式推理能力的统一多模态奖励模型，首次让奖励模型在各视觉任务上真正 “学会思考”，实现对复杂视觉生成与理解任务的准确评估、跨任务泛化与推理可解释性的大幅提升。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1be8b639-06cb-40be-f6d1-d74b684ad400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24436741767764297\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1154\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100010999\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1be8b639-06cb-40be-f6d1-d74b684ad400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3840f509-ef0d-48b1-c956-0ab9e4e42000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5432900432900433\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"924\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100011000\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3840f509-ef0d-48b1-c956-0ab9e4e42000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">一、背景与动机：奖励模型也需要 “思考”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当前的多模态奖励模型大多只能对结果进行 “表面判断”，缺乏深度推理与可解释的决策依据，难以支撑对复杂视觉任务的精准评估。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">该工作研究团队提出关键问题：是否可以引入 “长链式思考”（Chain-of-Thought, CoT）机制，赋予奖励模型更强的推理能力？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">挑战在于，当前缺乏高质量的多模态 CoT 奖励推理数据，传统 SFT 等训练范式难以直接教会模型掌握推理过程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他们认为，多模态大模型本身具备深层、多维度的推理潜力，关键在于设计一套高效训练范式去激发并强化奖励模型的 “思考能力”。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/95e2b67f-8ddb-4bc4-f9e4-5d39ac0af800/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8018518518518518\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503484776\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/95e2b67f-8ddb-4bc4-f9e4-5d39ac0af800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">二、解决方案：三阶段训练范式，逐步进化奖励模型推理能力</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">该研究提出一套新颖的 “三阶段” 训练框架，分为 “激发 → 巩固 → 强化”，层层推进模型的推理进化：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">阶段一：冷启动激发（Cold Start）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">使用仅 5K 图像生成任务的高质量 CoT 奖励推理数据，让模型学会基本的推理格式与结构。实验表明，这一阶段就能激发模型在多个视觉任务中的推理能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">阶段二：拒绝采样巩固（Rejection Sampling）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">利用冷启动后的模型在各视觉任务的泛化能力，对大规模多模态偏好数据进行推理，通过拒绝采样剔除逻辑错误样本，强化模型对正确思维链的推理模式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">阶段三：GRPO 强化（Group Relative Policy Optimization）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">针对推理错误样本，引入 GRPO 强化学习机制，引导模型探索多样化推理路径，从错误中学习，逐步收敛到正确逻辑思考。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">三、实验亮点：奖励模型不仅能 “显示长链推理”，还能 “隐式逻辑思考”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">UnifiedReward-Think 在多个图像生成与理解任务中进行了系统评估，结果表明该模型具备多项突破性能力：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更强可解释性：能够生成清晰、结构化的奖励推理过程；</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更高可靠性与泛化能力：各视觉任务均表现出显著性能提升；</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">出现隐式推理能力：即使不显式输出思维链，模型也能作出高质量判断，表明推理逻辑已 “内化” 为模型能力的一部分。</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">定量实验：长链推理带来全面性能飞跃</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/172e8539-5a1f-42af-6494-1cbce839b800/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6842592592592592\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503484779\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/172e8539-5a1f-42af-6494-1cbce839b800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">定量结果表明</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在图像与视频生成奖励任务中，全面优于现有方法；</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在图像理解类奖励任务上，长链思维链推理带来显著性能提升，验证了复杂视觉理解对深度推理能力的高度依赖；</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">即便在不显式输出思维链的情况下，模型仍能通过隐式逻辑推理保持领先表现，相比显式 CoT 推理仅有轻微下降，展现出强大的 “内化逻辑” 能力；</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">与基础版本 UnifiedReward 相比，加入多维度、多步骤推理带来了多任务的全面性能跃升，验证了 “奖励模型也能深度思考” 的价值。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">消融实验：三阶段训练策略缺一不可</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">该工作进行了系统的消融实验，验证三阶段训练范式中每一步的独立贡献：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">冷启动阶段：模型学会了 CoT 推理的结构，但对奖励预测的准确性仍较有限；</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">拒绝采样阶段：通过筛除推理错误样本，显著提升了模型对 “正确思维链” 的偏好，有效增强了模型的稳定性与泛化性；</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">GRPO 阶段：提升幅度最大，模型聚焦于错误推理样本，通过多路径推理探索，逐步收敛至更精确的推理过程，体现出该阶段对 “推理纠错” 的关键作用。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">无推理路径的 GRPO 版本效果显著下降。我们进一步验证：若去除 CoT 推理、让奖励模型仅对最终答案进行 GRPO 强化，虽然略优于 baseline，但提升比较有限。说明仅优化结果远不足以驱动深层推理能力的形成。</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">结论：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">显式建模思维链推理路径，是强化奖励模型泛化与鲁棒性的关键。GRPO 训练阶段之所以有效，根源在于 “强化正确推理过程”，而非仅仅是 “强化正确答案”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d5e9bb9e-5434-4298-dad8-91cb87cef300/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6861111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503484780\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d5e9bb9e-5434-4298-dad8-91cb87cef300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d1ecb73b-42c1-4c38-a6bd-6b0dbfbe2200/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6972222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 497px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503484781\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d1ecb73b-42c1-4c38-a6bd-6b0dbfbe2200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">定性效果展示</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">该工作在多种视觉任务中对模型进行了案例测试，展现出其按任务定制评估维度的能力。通过对图像、视频或答案进行细粒度、多维度打分，并基于各维度总分进行整体判断。此设计有效缓解了多模态模型中常见的 “推理过程与最终评分语义脱节” 问题，显著提升了评估的一致性与可信度。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6e58f89-2368-4f18-ade0-b4b6ed920100/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7898148148148149\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503484782\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6e58f89-2368-4f18-ade0-b4b6ed920100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d042e50a-2883-455a-056a-9b9c4e1b7e00/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.9768518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503484783\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d042e50a-2883-455a-056a-9b9c4e1b7e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a98c4ab4-3fbb-4d8d-c415-6bdea672e400/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503484784\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a98c4ab4-3fbb-4d8d-c415-6bdea672e400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/17cbc8b7-6d8e-438b-28ba-3ad4db542b00/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8314814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503484785\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/17cbc8b7-6d8e-438b-28ba-3ad4db542b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/aa871761-53b7-4c2d-2baa-714128c69500/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.2083333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503484787\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/aa871761-53b7-4c2d-2baa-714128c69500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/418c0f94-2595-4989-7443-76f3d93e6200/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.1555555555555554\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503484788\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/418c0f94-2595-4989-7443-76f3d93e6200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">四：总结</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">UnifiedReward-Think 展示了奖励模型的未来方向 —— 不仅仅是一个 “打分器”，而是一个具备认知理解、逻辑推理与可解释输出能力的智能评估系统。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前，该项目已全面开源：包括模型、数据集、训练脚本与评测工具，欢迎社区研究者探索、复现与应用。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"color:#0052d9;font-size:12px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\">论文题目: Unified Multimodal Chain-of-Thought Reward Model through Reinforcement Fine-Tuning</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"color:#0052d9;font-size:12px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\">项目主页：https://codegoat24.github.io/UnifiedReward/think</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"color:#0052d9;font-size:12px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\">论文链接：https://arxiv.org/pdf/2505.03318</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"color:#0052d9;font-size:12px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\">GitHub：https://github.com/CodeGoat24/UnifiedReward</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"color:#0052d9;font-size:12px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\">模型：https://huggingface.co/collections/CodeGoat24/unifiedreward-models-67c3008148c3a380d15ac63a</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"color:#0052d9;font-size:12px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\">数据集：https://huggingface.co/collections/CodeGoat24/unifiedreward-training-data-67c300d4fd5eff00fa7f1ede</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b870052a-ee1e-48e6-cc2b-b24ddec46200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.7777777777777777\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100010993\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b870052a-ee1e-48e6-cc2b-b24ddec46200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "腾讯混元联合团队提出首个具备长链式推理能力的多模态奖励模型 UnifiedReward-Think 并全面开源，显著提升复杂视觉任务的评估能力与可解释性",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "腾讯混元联合团队提出首个具备长链式推理能力的多模态奖励模型 UnifiedReward-Think 并全面开源，显著提升复杂视觉任务的评估能力与可解释性",
  "summary": "文章介绍了腾讯混元与上海 AI Lab、复旦大学等机构联合提出的 UnifiedReward-Think 模型，这是首个具备长链式推理能力的统一多模态奖励模型。该模型通过创新的三阶段训练范式（冷启动激发、拒绝采样巩固、GRPO 强化），显著提升了奖励模型在复杂视觉任务中的评估能力、可解释性和泛化性能。消融实验验证了三阶段训练策略的必要性，特别是 GRPO 阶段对推理纠错的关键作用。实验结果表明，该模型不仅能生成清晰的推理过程，还具备隐式逻辑思考能力，有效解决了推理过程与最终评分语义脱节的问题，在图像与视频生成、理解等任务上全面优于现有方法。项目已全面开源模型、数据集、训练脚本和评测工具。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "首创具备长链式推理能力的多模态奖励模型",
      "explanation": "通过引入 CoT 机制，使奖励模型具备深度推理和可解释决策能力，解决了传统模型只能表面判断的问题"
    },
    {
      "point": "创新的三阶段训练范式",
      "explanation": "冷启动激发→拒绝采样巩固→GRPO 强化的渐进式训练方法，消融实验验证了各阶段的必要性，特别是 GRPO 对推理纠错的关键作用"
    },
    {
      "point": "显式与隐式推理能力并存",
      "explanation": "模型既能生成结构化推理过程，又能内化逻辑思考，在不显式输出思维链时仍保持高质量判断，解决了推理与评分语义脱节问题"
    },
    {
      "point": "全面性能提升",
      "explanation": "在图像生成、视频生成和图像理解等任务上均显著优于现有方法，验证了深度推理的价值"
    },
    {
      "point": "完整开源促进社区发展",
      "explanation": "开源模型、数据集、训练脚本和评测工具，为多模态奖励模型研究提供了宝贵资源和基准"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "奖励模型也需要'思考'，当前的多模态奖励模型大多只能对结果进行'表面判断'",
    "三阶段训练框架分为'激发→巩固→强化'，层层推进模型的推理进化",
    "GRPO 训练阶段之所以有效，根源在于'强化正确推理过程'，而非仅仅是'强化正确答案'",
    "通过对图像、视频或答案进行细粒度、多维度打分，有效缓解了多模态模型中常见的'推理过程与最终评分语义脱节'问题",
    "UnifiedReward-Think 展示了奖励模型的未来方向——不仅仅是一个'打分器'，而是一个具备认知理解、逻辑推理与可解释输出能力的智能评估系统"
